  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/400b6178d08d02381b1c33f375821570.avif?t=1708468125\" width=606 height=80 /></span><br>Polimines 2 combines Minesweeper and Nonograms for a captivating puzzle experience. Immerse yourself in a difficult game where logical thinking is key, and hidden patterns are everywhere.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/067a7673f9a81f70e94fbce80980339c.poster.avif?t=1708468125\" width=616 height=528 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/067a7673f9a81f70e94fbce80980339c.webm?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/067a7673f9a81f70e94fbce80980339c.mp4?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/1717279982c39cd2f73fccc7bd4fc0cd.avif?t=1708468125\" width=606 height=80 /></span><br>From the different layouts to each of the individual clues, every level has been meticulously hand crafted to be challenging and rewarding. Enjoy 60 levels, each with unique shapes and sizes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/b234d197a665ebf5eefa6cb86cd57c32.poster.avif?t=1708468125\" width=616 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/b234d197a665ebf5eefa6cb86cd57c32.webm?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/b234d197a665ebf5eefa6cb86cd57c32.mp4?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/71a9dcaef24b93df9b377e3753ad0eb3.avif?t=1708468125\" width=606 height=80 /></span><br>Every level in Polimines 2 can be solved without guessing. They have been tested numerous times to ensure that, unlike traditional Minesweeper, you never have to rely on luck to solve a level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/92b9e445e95ecd182d7a3edf6b1e7087.poster.avif?t=1708468125\" width=616 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/92b9e445e95ecd182d7a3edf6b1e7087.webm?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/92b9e445e95ecd182d7a3edf6b1e7087.mp4?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/2dff1462386bb0dd3c3656e01df4764d.avif?t=1708468125\" width=606 height=80 /></span><br>With no timers to rush you and its minimalist aesthetic, you can take your time solving each level. Take a break from the noise and distractions and find your own rhythm as you progress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/5d9e18fac60203fa66682afb1d7fd16c.poster.avif?t=1708468125\" width=616 height=464 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/5d9e18fac60203fa66682afb1d7fd16c.webm?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/5d9e18fac60203fa66682afb1d7fd16c.mp4?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/400b6178d08d02381b1c33f375821570.avif?t=1708468125\" width=606 height=80 /></span><br>Polimines 2 combines Minesweeper and Nonograms for a captivating puzzle experience. Immerse yourself in a difficult game where logical thinking is key, and hidden patterns are everywhere.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/067a7673f9a81f70e94fbce80980339c.poster.avif?t=1708468125\" width=616 height=528 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/067a7673f9a81f70e94fbce80980339c.webm?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/067a7673f9a81f70e94fbce80980339c.mp4?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/1717279982c39cd2f73fccc7bd4fc0cd.avif?t=1708468125\" width=606 height=80 /></span><br>From the different layouts to each of the individual clues, every level has been meticulously hand crafted to be challenging and rewarding. Enjoy 60 levels, each with unique shapes and sizes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/b234d197a665ebf5eefa6cb86cd57c32.poster.avif?t=1708468125\" width=616 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/b234d197a665ebf5eefa6cb86cd57c32.webm?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/b234d197a665ebf5eefa6cb86cd57c32.mp4?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/71a9dcaef24b93df9b377e3753ad0eb3.avif?t=1708468125\" width=606 height=80 /></span><br>Every level in Polimines 2 can be solved without guessing. They have been tested numerous times to ensure that, unlike traditional Minesweeper, you never have to rely on luck to solve a level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/92b9e445e95ecd182d7a3edf6b1e7087.poster.avif?t=1708468125\" width=616 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/92b9e445e95ecd182d7a3edf6b1e7087.webm?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/92b9e445e95ecd182d7a3edf6b1e7087.mp4?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/2dff1462386bb0dd3c3656e01df4764d.avif?t=1708468125\" width=606 height=80 /></span><br>With no timers to rush you and its minimalist aesthetic, you can take your time solving each level. Take a break from the noise and distractions and find your own rhythm as you progress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/5d9e18fac60203fa66682afb1d7fd16c.poster.avif?t=1708468125\" width=616 height=464 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/5d9e18fac60203fa66682afb1d7fd16c.webm?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328730/extras/5d9e18fac60203fa66682afb1d7fd16c.mp4?t=1708468125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
